# EstateFlow

- Stack: FastAPI + LangGraph + Supabase + React/Vite
- No hardcoded business data; load from Supabase
- Complaints via platform portal (not WhatsApp intake)
- Maps: browser geolocation + haversine vendor match; OSM/Nominatim only (no Google Maps)
- LLM: OpenRouter primary, Ollama optional fallback
- Maintenance pipeline: security → complaint → priority → compliance → vendor_matching → governance → scheduling → communications → report_agent → performance_agent; predictive_maintenance_agent runs weekly async
- Roles: tenant, manager, inspector, admin (profiles table)
- Log all agent runs to agent_logs table
